      public void mergeSection(@NotNull @NotNull String key, @NotNull @NotNull DataStorage section, boolean overwrite)
      Merge another DataStorage into this DataStorage as a section.
      This means if you merge "section1.section2" into this DataStorage with key "section0", the value in this DataStorage will be "section0.section1.section2".
      Parameter:
      key - section key
      section - section
      overwrite - when true, existing values will be replaced (recommended)
